Pink Ladies said Coster, 38, from Hanover Park, was living with her boyfriend in Belmont Park, Kraaifontein, and has been missing since July 1. Police spokesperson FC van Wyk said police are investigating. “Tania Coster was reported missing on August 11. It is alleged that she had been missing since July 1,” Van Wyk said. On its flyer, Pink Ladies said: “Recently, the family received a call from an unknown person to say that her life is in danger. It is unknown what she was wearing at the time.” Anyone with information may call Constable Matshisi on 0219805633, or Pink Ladies on 0722147439.